   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="translation">
            <ab>Heraklas to Hip[-], greeting. You will do well not to neglect the (matter) of Horos. So send at once the other 96 drachmas; and if you do not send them, come at once to me, since you are neglecting yourself. Many salutations to your father and all your household. Good-bye. (Addressed on the verso) Deliver to Ploutammon from - -</ab>
         </div>
